arStrings.szText: The Knights here suffer from a horrible vice, they call it the "Sacrament". Many seek confinement when their control slips. I've been imprisoned for speaking out against the practice.
It's as I said, Dmitriy. You've turned your back on your brethren. Captain Kharov commanded that all share in the Sacrament, or care for those who do as their minds are gloriously reshaped.
Release me, or I'll tear your heart out!
Your time is coming, brother! I've recorded your name for Kharov, you are to be his anointed! You shall find this "Neyrelle" and the prize she carries.
